\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1f53512998aa7a40eef0e7298a9e869d02ebcac219f1e5db4479ff48f5db936b?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g\' srcset=\'https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/1f53512998aa7a40eef0e7298a9e869d02ebcac219f1e5db4479ff48f5db936b?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x\' class=\'avatar avatar-16 photo\' height=\'16\' width=\'16\' loading=\'lazy\' decoding=\'async\'/></a><a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/mochtafeez/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">mochtafeez</a> le <span class=\"review-date\">novembre 7, 2025</span>			</p>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<div class=\"review-body\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>WooCommerce has completely transformed the way I run my online store. The integration with WordPress is seamless, and the flexibility it offers is unmatched. From customizable product pages to a wide range of plugins and payment gateways, everything just works. The user interface is intuitive, and even as a non-developer, I was able to set up my store with ease. Support from the community and documentation is top-notch. Highly recommended for anyone serious about building a professional online shop!</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n	<div class=\"review-head\">\n		<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n			<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n				<h4 class=\"review-title\">Fast and reliable support</h4>\n				<div class=\"star-rating\">\n				<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 sur 5 étoiles\" data-title-template=\"%s sur 5 étoiles\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"></span></div>				</div>\n			</div>\n			<p class=\"reviewer\">\n				Par <a href=\"https://profiles.wordpress.org/luniumlondon/\"><img alt=\'\' src=\'https:/